Package com.hardgforgif.dragonboatracing.UI

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ChoosingUI
    The UI class for the player to choose a boat to race with, extends from UI.
    GameOverUI
    UI class for the end of the game, extends UI.
    GamePlayUI
    The UI during gameplay (racing), extends UI.
    MenuUI
    Class representing a main menu for the game, extends UI.
    ResultsUI
    Class representing the UI for displaying the results of each leg, extends UI.
    ScrollingBackground
    Displays a scrolling background, used for menu backgrounds.
    UI
    An abstract class from which to extend concrete UI classes.
